Legion_of_Super-Heroes_-_Enemy_Manifest_(2009-05)_TPB_(digital)_(OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD) 


While war looms and a traitor plots against the Legion from within, a massive, hostile planet appears near Jupiter, and its gravity is ripping apart the solar system! Collecting LEGION OF SUPER-HEROES #45-50 from legendary LEGION writer Jim Shooter and artist Francis Manapul (Witchblade).
